      "rationale": "A three-level mesh refinement study was performed on the pedicle screw shank and rod interface regions. Stiffness QoI changed by 1.3% between medium and fine meshes. Richardson extrapolation yielded a discretization error estimate of 0.9%, well within the 2% threshold."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
