      "rationale": "The validation scenario uses the identical non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw geometry, Ti-6Al-4V material, ASTM F1717 test fixture, and compression-bending load case as the COU. No extrapolation in geometry or material is required. The validation activities are directly relevant to the intended regulatory use."
    }
